\begin_layout Standard
对于给定电子能级间的跃迁, 由于可同时伴随振动能级和转动能级间的变化, 故分子光谱比较复杂, 它不同于线状的原子光谱, 而是以带状出现。故分子光谱是带状光谱。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
并不是任意两个能级间都能发生跃迁而产生光谱。光谱的产生是光和物质相互作用的结果, 即光和物质分子运动相互作用的结果。下面我们将用一种近似方法——微扰理论来处理它
。完善的理论是要把光的辐射场和分子运动都量子化。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
微扰理论
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在光的照射下, 分子可能吸收光而从较低能级跃迁到较高能级, 这种现象称为光的吸收, 分子也可在光的照射下, 从较高的能级跃迁到较低的能级而发射出光,
 这种现象称为受激辐射; 而且, 即使没有光的照射, 处于激发能级的分子也能自发地跃迁到较低能级而发射出光来, 这称为自发辐射。在光谱中, 有两个重要的观测量—
—谱线的频率和谱线的强度。由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-3"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式准谱线的频率与始态和末态的能量差有关, 而谱线的强度出跃迁几率决定。光和分子的相互作用, 可以近似地把光看成是对分子体系的一种微扰。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
当体系在含时间微扰
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{H}'(t)$
\end_inset

作用下, 体系的总Hamilton算符
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{H}(t)$
\end_inset

是未受微扰体系不含时间的Hamilton算符
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{H}_{0}$
\end_inset

。和与时间有关的微扰算符
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{H}'(t)$
\end_inset

的和, 即
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{H}(t)=\hat{H}_{0}+\hat{H}'(t)\label{eq:7-7}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{H}_{0}$
\end_inset

算符的本征值和本征函数为已知, 即
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\hat{H}_{0}\varPhi_{n} & \text{＝}i\hslash\frac{\partial\varPhi_{n}}{\partial t}\label{eq:7-8}\\
\varPhi_{n} & =\phi_{n}\exp\left(-\frac{i}{\hslash}E_{n}t\right)\label{eq:7-9}\\
\hat{H}_{0}\phi_{n} & =E_{n}\phi_{n}\label{eq:7-10}
\end{align}

\end_inset

式中
\begin_inset Formula $\hslash=\frac{h}{2\pi}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{H}'(t)$
\end_inset

与时间有关, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{H}(t)$
\end_inset

随时间而改变, 体系的能量不是守恒量, 它不处在定态。我们要求含时间的Schrodinger方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
i\hslash\frac{\partial\psi}{\partial t}=\hat{H}\psi=\left(\hat{H}_{0}+\hat{H}'\right)\psi\label{eq:7-11}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

的解也为
\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

。将
\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

以
\begin_inset Formula $\varPhi_{n}$
\end_inset

展开
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\psi=\sum_{n}a_{n}(t)\varPhi_{n}\label{eq:7-12}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}(t)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{2}(t)$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $···$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{n}(t)$
\end_inset

是和时间
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

有关的系数, 为了求出
\begin_inset Formula $a_{n}(t)$
\end_inset

, 可将(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-12"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式代入(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-11"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式, 即得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
i\hslash\sum_{n}\left(a_{n}\frac{\partial\varPhi_{n}}{\partial t}+\varPhi_{n}\frac{\partial a_{n}}{\partial t}\right)=\sum_{n}a_{n}\hat{H}_{0}\varPhi_{n}+\sum_{n}a_{n}\hat{H}'\varPhi_{n}
\]

\end_inset

由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-8"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式消除上式两端的第一个求和项, 得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
i\hslash\sum_{n}\varPhi_{n}\frac{da_{n}}{dt}=\sum_{n}a_{n}\hat{H}'\varPhi_{n}\label{eq:7-13}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

以
\begin_inset Formula $\varPhi_{m}^{*}$
\end_inset

左乘(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-13"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式两边, 并对整个空间积分, 同时注意到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\int\varPhi_{m}^{*}\varPhi_{n}d\tau=\begin{cases}
0 & m\neq n\\
1 & m=n
\end{cases}\label{eq:7-14}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

就可得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
i\hslash\frac{da_{m}}{dt}=\sum_{n}H'_{mn}a_{n}\exp\left(i\omega_{mn}t\right)\label{eq:7-15}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

式中
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
H'_{mn} & =\int\varPhi_{m}^{*}\hat{H}'\varPhi_{n}d\tau\label{eq:7-16}\\
\omega_{mn} & =\frac{E_{m}-E_{n}}{\hslash}\label{eq:7-17}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\omega_{mn}$
\end_inset

是体系从
\begin_inset Formula $E_{n}$
\end_inset

能级跃迁到
\begin_inset Formula $E_{m}$
\end_inset

能级的玻尔频率。为解(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-15"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式, 引入参量
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

, 以
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\hat{H}'$
\end_inset

 , 代替
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{H}'$
\end_inset

, 并将
\begin_inset Formula $a_{n}(t)$
\end_inset

展开为
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

的幂级数, 即
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
a_{n}(t)=a_{n}^{(0)}+a_{n}^{(1)}\lambda+a_{n}^{(2)}\lambda^{2}+\cdots\label{eq:7-18}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

将上式代入(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-15"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
i\hslash\left\{ \frac{da_{m}^{(0)}}{dt}+\lambda\frac{da_{m}^{(1)}}{dt}+\lambda^{2}\frac{da_{m}^{(2)}}{dt}+\cdots\right\} =\sum_{n}\left(a_{n}^{(0)}+\lambda a_{n}^{(1)}+\lambda^{2}a_{n}^{(2)}+\cdots\right)\lambda H'_{mn}\exp\left(i\omega_{mn}t\right)
\]

\end_inset

令上式中
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

的同次幂相等, 可得微分方程组:  
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left\{ \begin{split}\frac{da_{m}^{(0)}}{dt} & =0\\
\frac{da_{m}^{(1)}}{dt} & =\frac{1}{i\hslash}\sum_{n}H'_{mn}a_{n}^{(0)}\exp\left(i\omega_{mn}t\right)\\
\frac{da_{m}^{(2)}}{dt} & =\frac{1}{i\hslash}\sum_{n}H'_{mn}a_{n}^{(1)}\exp\left(i\omega_{mn}t\right)\\
\cdots & \cdots
\end{split}
\right.\label{eq:7-19}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

解方程组(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-19"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

), 可以求得(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-12"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式中
\begin_inset Formula $a_{n}$
\end_inset

的各级近似解, 从而得到波函数的近似解。实际上, 在大多数情况下, 求得第一级近似解就巳经足够了。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
光的吸收和发射
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-19"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式中, 由
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{da_{m}^{(0)}}{dt}=0$
\end_inset

说明
\begin_inset Formula $a_{m}^{(0)}$
\end_inset

是不随时间而变化的, 它是由微扰前的初态决定的。若初态为
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{k}$
\end_inset

则对所有的
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

均有
\begin_inset Formula $a_{m}^{(0)}=\delta_{mk}=\begin{cases}
0 & m\neq k\\
1 & m=k
\end{cases}$
\end_inset

。当只考虑到一级近似时, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{m}=a_{m}^{(0)}+a_{m}^{(1)}=\delta_{mk}+a_{m}^{(1)}
\]

\end_inset

由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-12"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式, 这时体系波函数
\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\psi=a_{1}^{(1)}\varPhi_{1}+a_{2}^{(1)}\varPhi_{2}+\cdots+(1+a_{k}^{(1)})\varPhi_{k}+\cdots+a_{n}^{(1)}\varPhi_{n}+\cdots\label{eq:7-20}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

由态迭加原理可知
\begin_inset Formula $\left|a_{m}^{(1)}(t)\right|^{2}$
\end_inset

表示本系处在本征态
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{m}$
\end_inset

的几率, 若初态为
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{k}$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\left|a_{m}^{(1)}\right|^{2}$
\end_inset

实际上就是由
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{k}$
\end_inset

跃迁到
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{m}$
\end_inset

的跃迁几率。由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-19"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式和
\begin_inset Formula $a_{n}^{(0)}=\delta_{nk}$
\end_inset

可得
\begin_inset Formula 
