\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\chi(\boldsymbol{R})$
\end_inset

仅与核的坐标有关, 代入方程 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-45"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
-\sum_{p}\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m_{p}}\psi\nabla_{p}^{2}\chi-\sum_{p}\frac{\hslash^{2}}{m_{p}}\nabla_{p}\psi\cdot\nabla_{p}\chi-\sum_{p}\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m_{p}}\chi\nabla_{p}^{2}\psi-\sum_{i}\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m}\chi\nabla_{i}^{2}\psi+V(\boldsymbol{R},\boldsymbol{r})\psi\chi=E\psi\chi\label{eq:7-47}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

对通常分子, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\frac{m_{p}}{m} & \approx10^{3}\text{--}10^{5}\label{eq:7-48}\\
\nabla_{p}\psi\cdot\nabla_{p}\chi & \approx\chi\nabla_{i}^{2}\psi\label{eq:7-49}\\
\nabla_{p}^{2}\psi & \approx\nabla_{i}^{2}\psi\label{eq:7-50}
\end{align}

\end_inset

这样, 方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-47"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)中左边第二项和第三项比起第四项来, 就可忽略, 从而得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
-\sum_{p}\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m_{p}}\psi\nabla_{p}^{2}\chi-\sum_{i}\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m}\chi\nabla_{i}^{2}\psi+V(\boldsymbol{R},\boldsymbol{r})\psi\chi=E\psi\chi\label{eq:7-51}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

方程 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-51"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 可以分离变量化为以下两个方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
-\sum_{i}\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m}\nabla_{i}^{2}\psi(\boldsymbol{R},\boldsymbol{r})+V(\boldsymbol{R},\boldsymbol{r})\psi(\boldsymbol{R},\boldsymbol{r})=E(\boldsymbol{R})\psi(\boldsymbol{R},\boldsymbol{r})\label{eq:7-52}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
-\sum_{p}\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m_{p}}\nabla_{p}^{2}\chi(\boldsymbol{R})+E(\boldsymbol{R})\chi(\boldsymbol{R})=E\chi(\boldsymbol{R})\label{eq:7-53}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-52"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-53"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式中的
\begin_inset Formula $E(\boldsymbol{R})$
\end_inset

是分离变量中出现的常数。为了避免混淆, 总能虽
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

用
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon$
\end_inset

表示, (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-53"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)变为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
-\sum_{p}\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m_{p}}\nabla_{p}^{2}\chi+E(R)\chi=\epsilon\chi\label{eq:7-54}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

方程, (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-52"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)为在某种固定核的位置时体系的电子运动方程。方程(
