\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{d^{2}R(q)}{dq^{2}}+\left[\frac{\alpha}{\beta}+q^{2}\right]R(q)=0\label{eq:7-91}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

式中
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

为无量纲的量。方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-91"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)的解
\begin_inset Formula $R(q)$
\end_inset

必须满足标准化条件, 即当
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

从
\begin_inset Formula $-\infty$
\end_inset

到
\begin_inset Formula $+\infty$
\end_inset

时, 
\begin_inset Formula $R(q)$
