\end{equation}

\end_inset

此时方程的特解为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
R(q)=e^{\pm\frac{q^{2}}{2}}\label{eq:7-93}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

因为当
\begin_inset Formula $q\rightarrow+\infty$
\end_inset

