a_{n+2}=\frac{-2\left(v-n\right)}{\left(n+2\right)\left(n+1\right)}a_{n}\label{eq:7-114}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

因为
\begin_inset Formula $u(q)$
\end_inset

是二阶微分方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-95"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)的解, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $u(q)$
\end_inset

可有两个任意选定的积分常数。一般把
\begin_inset Formula $a_{0}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}$
\end_inset

作为积分常数, 而且约定当
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

为偶数时, 令
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{1}=0,a_{0}=(-1)^{\frac{v}{2}}v!/\left(\frac{v}{2}\right)!
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

为奇数时, 令
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{0}=0,a_{1}=2\cdot(-1)^{\frac{v-1}{2}}v!/\left(\frac{v-1}{2}\right)!
\]

\end_inset

