振动能级间的能量差, 则
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
D=E_{v_{c}}=\left(\frac{1}{2\chi}+\frac{1}{2}\right)hc\widetilde{\omega}-\left(\frac{1}{2\chi}+\frac{1}{2}\right)^{2}hc\widetilde{\omega}\chi\approx\frac{1}{4\chi}hc\widetilde{\omega}\label{eq:7-185}
\end{equation}

