\begin_layout Standard
如果只考虑振动能级间的跃迁, 谱线应是一条条分离的谱线。但用分辨率高的光谱仪观察, 每一条振动谱“线”是由若干条谱线组成的谱带。谱带内各谱线的波数可用经验公式
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\widetilde{\nu}=c+dm+em^{2},\qquad m=\pm1,\pm2,\pm3,\cdots\label{eq:7-189}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

表示。这称为谱带的精细结构, 是由于振–转相互作用的结果。由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-146"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 和 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-163"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 振－转能级为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
E_{v,J}=\left(v+\frac{1}{2}\right)hc\widetilde{\omega}-\left(v+\frac{1}{2}\right)^{2}hc\widetilde{\omega}\chi+J(J+1)hcB-J^{2}(J+1)^{2}hcD-\left(v+\frac{1}{2}\right)J(J+!)hc\alpha+\cdots\label{eq:7-190}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

式中最后一项为振–转相互作用项, 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

为振–转作用常数。(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-190"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式可写为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
E_{v,J}=\left(v+\frac{1}{2}\right)hc\widetilde{\omega}-\left(v+\frac{1}{2}\right)^{2}hc\widetilde{\omega}\chi+J(J+1)hc\left[B-\alpha\left(v+\frac{1}{2}\right)\right]-J^{2}(J+1)^{2}hcD+\cdots\label{eq:7-191}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

令
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
B_{v}=B-\alpha\left(v+\frac{1}{2}\right)+\cdots\label{eq:7-192}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

并考虑到转动的非刚性能量部分比振动的非谐性部分小得多, 略去 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7-191"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

