E=\frac{1}{2}\sum_{i=1}^{s}(\frac{1}{c_{ii}}P_{i}^{2}+d_{ii}Q_{i}^{2})\label{eq:7-290}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

运动方程可从 Newton 第二定律推出, 
